  <summary date="2021-03-29T14:36:13Z" status="Introduced in House">Gold Star Altitude Act

This bill authorizes the Department of Defense to offer, on a space-available basis, transportation on military aircraft to the children, surviving spouses, parents, and siblings of members of the Armed Forces who die during active service.</summary>
